## **6. Microsoft.Extensions.AI: AIFunction & AITool**

### **AIFunction** - Represents a callable function:
```csharp
public abstract class AIFunction
{
    // Properties
    public virtual MethodInfo UnderlyingMethod { get; } // .NET method info
    public virtual JsonSerializerOptions JsonSerializerOptions { get; }

    // Implement InvokeAsync to invoke the function with arguments
